stories.title: Pakistan win first match of the series by 7 runs
stories.summary: It looked like one of the most one-sided of one-day matches at Queens Sports Club in Bulawayo when Pakistan ran up 302 for four and then removed four Zimbabwe batsmen for just 32 runs
